-# ==================== HERO ====================
.hero.py-20.bg-base-200
  .hero-content.text-center
    .max-w-3xl
      %h1.text-5xl.font-bold Bethel Christian Daycare
      %p.py-6.text-xl.italic.opacity-80
        &ldquo;Growing Children in Christian Knowledge and Love&rdquo;

-# ==================== MISSION STATEMENT ====================
.bg-primary.text-primary-content.py-12
  .max-w-4xl.mx-auto.px-4.text-center
    %p.text-2xl.font-semibold
      Welcome! Our mission is to provide for your child a safe-haven full of love and fun in a
      Christ-centered, caring environment.

