-# ==================== OUR PROGRAMS ====================
.bg-base-200.py-16
  .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4
    %h2.text-4xl.font-bold.text-center.mb-4 Our Programs
    %p.text-center.opacity-70.mb-12.max-w-3xl.mx-auto
      Our facility emphasizes early childhood education foundations grounded in Christian values.
      Key classroom goals include:
    .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-2.lg:grid-cols-3.gap-6
      - [['Spiritual Growth', 'Developing awareness of God and a personal need for Him'], ['Health & Safety', 'Developing safe and healthy habits'], ['Independence', 'Fostering positive independence'], ['Creative Expression', 'Providing opportunities for creative expression'], ['Social Skills', 'Supporting social skills development'], ['Problem Solving', 'Stimulating cognitive problem-solving abilities'], ['Communication', 'Strengthening listening, reading, writing, and speaking skills'], ['Motor Skills', 'Enhancing fine and gross motor skills'], ['Individual Needs', "Assessing and supporting each child's individual needs"]].each do |title, description|
        .flex.items-start.gap-3.p-4.bg-base-100.rounded-box.shadow
          %svg.h-6.w-6.text-primary.shrink-0.mt-0.5{ xmlns: "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg", fill: "none", viewBox: "0 0 24 24", stroke: "currentColor" }
            %path{ "stroke-linecap" => "round", "stroke-linejoin" => "round", "stroke-width" => "2", d: "M5 13l4 4L19 7" }
          .space-y-1
            %h3.font-semibold= title
            %p.text-sm.opacity-70= description
    .text-center.mt-10
      .badge.badge-primary.badge-lg.p-4.mt-4
        Curriculum: Children Desiring God Bible Curriculum &amp; Abeka Preschool Program
      %p.mt-4.opacity-70.italic Parent participation is always welcome!

-# ==================== OUR STAFF ====================
.bg-base-100.py-16
  .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4
    .grid.grid-cols-1.lg:grid-cols-2.gap-12.items-center
      .space-y-6
        %h2.text-4xl.font-bold Our Staff
        %p.opacity-80
          Our staff members possess significant experience and training in young children&rsquo;s care.
          All employees must meet the following requirements:
        %ul.space-y-3
          - ['Background checks', 'Physical exam', 'TB test', 'Hepatitis A vaccine', 'CPR/First-Aid training'].each do |req|
            %li.flex.items-center.gap-3
              %svg.h-5.w-5.text-primary.shrink-0{ xmlns: "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg", fill: "none", viewBox: "0 0 24 24", stroke: "currentColor" }
                %path{ "stroke-linecap" => "round", "stroke-linejoin" => "round", "stroke-width" => "2", d: "M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" }
              %span= req
      .card.bg-base-200.shadow-lg
        .card-body.items-center.text-center
          %svg.h-24.w-24.text-primary.mb-4{ xmlns: "http://www.w3.org/2000/svg", fill: "none", viewBox: "0 0 24 24", stroke: "currentColor" }
            %path{ "stroke-linecap" => "round", "stroke-linejoin" => "round", "stroke-width" => "1.5", d: "M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" }
          %h3.card-title.text-xl Experienced &amp; Trained
          %p.opacity-70
            Every member of our team is dedicated to providing the best care in a
            Christ-centered environment.

